ICD-10-PCS Rows

Source: R/tables.R
rows.Rd

ICD-10-PCS Rows

Usage

rows(x = NULL)

Arguments

x

3 to 4-character string representing an ICD-10-PCS row within a table. If NULL (default), returns all ~ 29k rows.

Value

a tibble

Examples

rows("00X")
#> # A tibble: 12 × 5
#>    table row   description                       rowid axes             
#>    <chr> <chr> <chr>                             <int> <named list>     
#>  1 00X   00XF  Body Part, Olfactory Nerve           38 <tibble [15 × 4]>
#>  2 00X   00XG  Body Part, Optic Nerve               38 <tibble [15 × 4]>
#>  3 00X   00XH  Body Part, Oculomotor Nerve          38 <tibble [15 × 4]>
#>  4 00X   00XJ  Body Part, Trochlear Nerve           38 <tibble [15 × 4]>
#>  5 00X   00XK  Body Part, Trigeminal Nerve          38 <tibble [15 × 4]>
#>  6 00X   00XL  Body Part, Abducens Nerve            38 <tibble [15 × 4]>
#>  7 00X   00XM  Body Part, Facial Nerve              38 <tibble [15 × 4]>
#>  8 00X   00XN  Body Part, Acoustic Nerve            38 <tibble [15 × 4]>
#>  9 00X   00XP  Body Part, Glossopharyngeal Nerve    38 <tibble [15 × 4]>
#> 10 00X   00XQ  Body Part, Vagus Nerve               38 <tibble [15 × 4]>
#> 11 00X   00XR  Body Part, Accessory Nerve           38 <tibble [15 × 4]>
#> 12 00X   00XS  Body Part, Hypoglossal Nerve         38 <tibble [15 × 4]>

rows("00XF")
#> # A tibble: 1 × 5
#>   table row   description                rowid axes             
#>   <chr> <chr> <chr>                      <int> <named list>     
#> 1 00X   00XF  Body Part, Olfactory Nerve    38 <tibble [15 × 4]>
